name: Floral Graffiti
description:
This textual inversion (TI) adds pastel colours, floral patterns and geometric motifs. I trained it using photographs of spray-painted street art from my local area. It has a tendency to create symmetrical compositions and a strong preference for circles and curves over straight lines and right-angles.

The TI does well at paintings and stylised images, but I have also had good results with photorealistic outputs.
